<!-- <title>Previo a la unidad</title> -->
<!-- <title>Exploración</title> -->
<!-- <title component="metadata">Alineado con <xref ref="graVV-uniYY-secZZ" text="title"/></title> -->
<title component="metadata">Alineado con <xref ref="lec-VVVVVV" text="title"/></title>

<statement>
  <p>Ubica y marca el 1 en la recta numérica. Explica cómo razonaste.</p>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-151743">
    <shortdescription>Number line. Tick marks labeled 0 and 5 thirds.</shortdescription>
  </image>
</statement>

<solution>
  <p>[++++++++++++++++++++]</p>
  <image source="svg-source/tikz-file-152496">
    <shortdescription>Number line.</shortdescription>
  </image>
  <p>Sample response: Since there are 5 thirds in <m>\frac{5}{3}</m> I broke the space from 0 to <m>\frac{5}{3}</m> into 5 equal pieces and each of those is <m>\frac{1}{3}</m>. The third tick is 1 because there are 3 thirds in a whole.</p>
</solution>

</exercise>
